  I. 2002. 11.14 
  2002 ni5 11 goeh8 14 jit8, pai3-si3. Cha2-khi2 9-tiam2-goa7, goa2 ka7 140 hun7 e5 Eng-gi2 ki5-tiong-kho2 kho2-chhi3-choa2 teng3 ho2-se3, chun2-pi7 beh khi3 kau3-sek kam3-kho2. Tu2-ho2 keng-koe3 Thong-sek Tiong-sim, siuN7-kong2 chin-ku2 bo5-khi3 sun5 goa2 e5 sin3-siuN, sun7-soa3 oat-jip8-khi3 khoaN3-mai7. Kiat-kiok8 ti7 tiaN7-tiaN7 khang-long2-long2 e5 sin3-siuN-lai7, theh8-tioh8 au7-hak8-ki5 e5 thong-sek-kho3 sin-chheng2-pio2. Che-si7 teng2-le2-pai3 pai3 5, goa2 E-mail chhut--khi3, ui7-tioh8 goan5-lai5 e5 kho3-theng5 the5-chhut e5 sin-chheng2-su. “Tai5-gi2 kap Bun5-hoa3” chit-e5-kho3 cha2 chiu7 ti7 2002 ni5 7--goeh8 hou7 Thong-sek Ui2-oan5-hoe7 thong-koe3, u7 theh8-tioh8 khui-kho3-koan5. Tiong5-sin sin-chheng2 put-ko3 si7 hou7 hak8-hau7 chai, lau7-su u7 i3-goan7 beh koh ka3, m7-bian2 koh hou7 Ui2-oan5-hoe7 sim2-cha. 
  Theh8-chhut chit-hun7 sin-chheng2-pio2, chiah hoat-hian7 i e7-te2 iau2-u7 chhiu2-sia2 e5 ji7, i3-su3 kong2, hak8-hau7 chhiaN3 kiam-jim7 lau7-su, kan-taN e7-sai2 ka3 i e5 choan-giap8 kho-bak8. 【本件退知鄭老師】Soa3-boe2 u7 hian7-jim7 Thong-sek Tiong-sim chu2-jim7 Jim7 Sian7-liong5 e5 chhiam-mia5. Goa2 khoaN3-liau2 kui-seng-khu phih8-phih8-chhoah, hoeh sui5 chheng3 kau3 thau5-khak-teng2. Koh eng7 teh-chun3 e5 siaN mng7 hiah-e5 chou7-li2, “I sia2 che si7 siaN2-mih8 i3-su3? Kio3 goa2 mai3-khui simh?” Chou7-li2 sio2-chia2 m7-bat khoaN3-koe3 goa2 chiah-nih8 siu7-khi3, it-tit8 ka7 goa2 he7 sit-le2, kong2-beh sui5 chhiaN2 in chu2-jim7 lai5. M7-ku2 chit8-si5 soah chhoe7 bo5 lang5. Goa2 ma7 in-ui7 hak8-seng beh kho2-chhi3 ai3 kin2 li7-khui. Chi2-ho2 iok ti7 kho2-liau2-au7 goa2 chiah koh lai5. 
  Hit-jit8 tiong-tau3, goa2 koh khi3 Thong-sek Tiong-sim. Chit-pai2 u7 chiap-tioh8 chu2-jim7 Jim7 Sian7-liong5. I si7 peng-a2 chhut-sin, ka3 tian7-chu2--e5, siN-cho3 san2-san2 lo3-lo3, tai7-iok 50 goa7 hoe3. In-ui7 i oan5-choan5 boe7-hiau2 kong2 Tai5-gi2, goa2 kou-put-chiong kap i kong2 pak-kiaN-oe7. Chit8-khai-si2, i kong2 u7-e5 lau7-su bo5 chiau3 kho3-theng5 kong-iau3 ka3 a7-si7 sng3 hun-sou3, in2-khi2 choe7-choe7 cheng-gi7. Goa2 kong2 che m7-si7 goa2 e5 bun7-te5, goa2 it-hiong3 hak8-ki5-thau5 chiu7 kap hak8-seng kau-tai3 chheng-chho2, ia7 long2 chiau3 iok-sok kiaN5. Jian5-au7 i koh kong2, u7 hak8-seng chau2-lai5 Thong-sek Tiong-sim ka7 in tau5, kong2 goa2 long2 iong7 Tai5-gi2 siong7-kho3, in boe7 koan3-si3. (Goa2 hoai5-gi5 kam2 u7 chit-chiong2 tai7-chi3? “Tai5-gi2 kap Bun5-hoa3” si7 chit-hak8-ki5 tu2 khui--e5. Tu2 ka3 poaN3-hak8-ki5, to iau2-boe7 cho3 pheng5-kam3, i na2 e7 chai? Ho5-hong3 kam2 u7 hak8-seng chiah8-pa2 hiah eng5, e7 ui7-tioh8 chit8-e5 soan2-siu e5 kho3, chau2-khi3 chhoe7 thong-sek tiong-sim e5 chu2-jim7?) Goa2 hoe5-tap, Tak8-chiong2-kho3 long2 u7 i e5 tiau5-kiaN7, iong7 Tai5-gi2 siong7-kho3 si7 khi2-thau5 chiu7 ka7 hak8-seng phin2-beng5--e5. Ji5-chhiaN2 che goan5-pun2 si7 soan2-siu e5 kho3, in na7 bo5 hoat-tou7 chiap-siu7 Tai5-gi2 siong7-kho3, ma7 iau2 e7-sai2 soan2 pat8-e5 kho3. Chit-si5, i soah hoan2-mng7 goa2, an2-ne kam2-si7 kio3 hak8-seng mai3 lai5 siong7--ah. Goa2 ka7 i kong2 m7-si7 chit-e5 i3-su3. 
  Chiap-soa3 chit-le2-pai3, hit-pan i kap ki5-tha e5 Tiong-kok-a2 hak8-sut8 lou5-moa5 long2-si7 iong7 chit-chiong2 khiu2-khiok, liah8-oe7-piN3 e5 khoan2-sit lai5 kong-kek--goa2. Goa2 koh ka7 i kong2, jim7-ho5 chit8-e5 kho3 to bo5 chai5-tiau7 hou7 sou2-u7 e5 hak8-seng boan2-i3. Kiam2-chhai2 u7 lang5 pai5-thiat iong7 Tai5-gi2 siong7-kho3. M7-ku2, tui3 khai-hak8 kau3 ka-the3-soan2 3 le2-pai3 tiong-kan, iau2 u7 59 e5 hak8-seng koat-teng7 beh lau5-loh8-lai5 ke3-siok8 oh8. Che tai7-piau2 chiok choe7 lang5 long2 hoaN-hi2 goa2 e5 siong7-kho3 hong-sek. Lun7 kau3 kau3-hak8 e5 gi2-gian5, goa2 ti7 chit-keng hak8-hau7 ma7 teh ka3 2 pan Eng-gi2. Tong-chhou hak8-hau7 iau3-kiu5 Eng-gi2 lau7-su ai3 iong7 Eng-gi2 siong7-kho3, thang eng5-cho7 gi2-gian5 khoan5-keng2. Chit-ma2 hak8-seng oh8 Tai5-gi2, iong7 Tai5-gi2 siong7-kho3, kam2 u7 siaN2-mih8 m7-tioh8? Jim7 Sian7-liong5 soa3--loh8 kong2, hian7-chhu2-si5 hak8-hau7 i2-keng teng7 sin e5 cheng3-chhek, kiam-jim7 lau7-su kan-ta e7 tang3 ka3 choan-giap8 kho-bak8. 
  I cha2 chiu7 tiau-cha goa2 tai7-hak8 kap gian2-kiu3-sou2 thak8 siaN2-mih, toa7-chu2-toa7-i3 jin7-teng7 goa2 bo5 chu-keh ka3 Tai5-gi2. I koh theh8 hau7-tiuN2 tng3-in3-a2 e5 kong-bun5 hou7 goa2 khoaN3. I koh na2 ka7 goa2 kong2, m7-na7 goa2 chit8-e5, iau2 u7 pat8-e5 lau7-su ma7 u7 chit-chiong2 ka3 “hui-choan-giap8 kho-bak8” e5 bun7-te5. Sou2-i2 thong-sek ui2-oan5-hoe7 beh ti7 au7-le2-pai3 3 khui-hoe7, tho2-lun7 in e5 kho3 au7-hak8-ki5 kam2 e7-sai2 koh khui. Chiah-e5 lau7-su ai3 chhut-sek8 soat-beng5. Chit-si5 goa2 chiah beng5-liau5, goan5-lai5 Jim7 Sian7-liong5 bo5 keng-koe3 ui2-oan5-hoe7, chiu7 su-te2-ha7 beh ka7 goa2 e5 kho3 “cho3-tiau7”. Si7 an2-choaN2 pat8-lang5 e7-tang3 the5-chhut soat-beng5, khiok ka7 goa2 chha-piat8 thai7-gu7, m7 hou7 goa2 peng5-teng2 e5 ki-hoe7? Kau3 chia lai5, i poe7-au7 e5 tong7-ki i2-keng chin beng5-hian2! 
  I koh kong2, chit-ma2 u7 Tai5-gi2-kho3, bo5 Kheh-gi2-kho3, kheh-lang5 na7 lai5 hoe beh an2-choaN2? Li2 si7 oh8 Eng-gi2 kap sin-bun5--e5. Na7 chin-chiaN3 beh ka3 Tai5-gi2 goa2 beh chhiaN3 Tiong-bun5-he7--e5. Goa2 ka7 i kong2, tui3-ti7 Tai5-gi2, Tiong-bun5 kap Eng-gi2 piN5-piN5 long2-si7 pat8-chiong2 gi2-gian5. Ki3-jian5 Tiong-bun5-he7--e5 e7-sai2 ka3, goa2 ia7 e7-sai2, chi2-si7 iong7 bo5-kang7 e5 khoan2-sit. I thiaN-tioh8 goa2 ka7 Tai5-gi2 kap Tiong-bun5 peng7-liat8 cho3 “Gi2-gian5”, bak8-thau5 sui5 kak-kak. Che ju2 cheng3-beng5 i ka7 Tai5-gi2 khoaN3-cho3 in Tiong-kok e5 hong-gian5, thiau-ti5 beh keng-the2, hoe3-tu5 Tai5-gi2-kho3. Jim7 Sian7-liong5 u7 mng7 goa2, kam2 beh khui sin-bun5 hong-bin7 e5 kho3, mai3 ka3 Tai5-gi2. Goa2 in3 i kong2, iau2 m7-bat siuN7-koe3 chit-e5 tai7-chi3. Choe3-au7 goa2 ka7 i kong2, goa2 beh ng3 Ui2-oan5-hoe7 soat-beng5. 
  II. 11. 20. 2002 
  Thau3-cha2 piaN3-khi3 Eng2-khong ka3 3 tiam2-cheng e5 kho3. E7-pou chheng2-ka2. 
  Thau3-tiong-tau3 chiu7 koaN2 kau3 Toa7-sia7, chun2-pi7 beh hu3 thong-sek ui2-oan5-hoe7 e5 hoe7-gi7, thang chhiuN2-kiu3 Tai5-gi2-kho3. 
  Sui-jian5 ai3 chiah8 tau3, khiok boe7 kam2-kak iau. In-ui7 liam5-mi chiu7 u7 chit8-tiuN5 khou2-chian3 ai3 phah, na2 u7 sim-cheng5 chiah8-png7? Su7-sit8-chiuN7 chit-le2-pai3 goa2 chha-put-to boe7 chiah8 boe7 khun3. Jit8--si5 chiau3-siong5 siong7-pan. Bo5-kho3 e5 si5 chiu7 si3-ke3 lian5-lok8 lang5, a2-si7 chhoan5 chu-liau7. Am3-si5 chhu3-lai7 khang-khoe3 cho3-soah, hoat-loh8 gin2-a2, kau2-a2 khi3-khun liau2-au7, ia7-si7 kang7-khoan2 kha3 tian7-oe7 chhoe7 lang5, cheng2-li2 chu-liau7. 
  Pun2-lai5 goa2 si7 chin ho2-khun3 e5 lang5, thau5 na7 khoeh-tioh8 chim2-thau5 chiu7 m7 chai lang5 ah. Chong2--si7 chit-cham7 u7-si5-chun7 kau3 2, 3 tiam2 iau2 khun3-boe7-khi3. Tek8-piat8 ti7 goa2 kap Jim7 Sian7-liong5 pian7-lun7, u7 kang7 hak8-hau7 e5 lau7-su khi3 tham3 i e5 oe7. I bo5 am-kham3 kong2--chhut-lai5, chiu7 si7 hoai5-gi5 goa2 iong7 Tai5-gi2-kho3 lai5 thoan5 Tai5-oan5 i3-sek. TaN chai-iaN2 i si7 ui7-tioh8 i3-sek heng5-thai3, chiah li7-iong7 chit-koan5, chioh heng5-cheng3 beng7-leng7 lai5 hoe3 Tai5-gi2-kho3, goa2 koat-sim beh kap i chian3 kau3 te2. 
  TiaN7-tiaN7 ti7 am3-mi5 teh-siuN7, chhin-chhiuN7 Jim7 Sian7-liong5 chiah-nih8 phian-kek e5 toa7-tiong-kok-chu2-gi7-chia2, chin-chiaN3 m7-si7 siau2-soat teh-sia2--e5. Ko2-jian5 hou7 goa2 chhin-sin tu2--tioh8. Kan-ta pin5 chit8-tiam2 hoai5-gi5 kap i3-sek heng5-thai3 bo5 kang7, i chiu7 tui3 chit8-e5 m7-bat khoaN3--koe3, bo5 sek8-sai7 koh kap i bo5 oan bo5 siu5 e5 lang5 he7 chit-khoan2 tok8-chhiu2. Ji5-chhiaN2 koh iong7 hiah-nih chhou-lou2 e5 hong-sek, boe7-su gong7-iong2 e5 kun-hu. Goa2 e5 kho3 si7 keng-koe3 sin-chheng2, teng2-kai3 e5 thong-sek ui2-oan5-hoe7 sou2 thong-koe3--e5. I choaN2 thang pin5 ko3-jin5 e5 i3-su3 chiu7 beh hoe3-tu5. Chit-e5 su7-kiaN7 i2-keng m7-si7 goa2 ko3-jin5 e5 li7-hai7 koan-he7 na7-tiaN7. Che si7 cheng3-ti7 phek-hai7! Si7 ah-pa3 e5 Tiong-kok soa-bun5 chu2-gi7-chia2 teh ki5-si7 Tai5-gi2, phek-hai7 Tai5-oan5-lang5 kap Tai5-oan5-bun5-hoa3! 
  Ju2 siuN7 chiu7 ju2 hun3-khai3. Tai5-oan5 i2-keng chiaN5-cho3 bin5-chu2 kok-ka. Hian7-chu2-si5, chong2-thong2 ia7 tioh8 Tai5-oan5-lang5 teh cho3. Keng3-jian5 iau2 u7 lang5 kaN2 iong7 chiah chhou-chhan5 e5 chhiu2-toaN7, lai5 hoan2-tui3 pun2-thou2-hoa3. Ong2-hui3 Tai5-oan5-bi2 teh hou7 in chiah8! 
  Cho3 chit8-e5 Tai5-oan5-lang5 goa2 boe7-eng7-e2 an2-ne chiu7 khut-hok8! Chun2-kong2 e7 an2-ne lai5 sit-khi3 thau5-lou7, ia7 beh kap Jim7 Sian7-liong5 chiah-e5 lang5 chian3 kau3-te2. Goa2 chai hak8-hau7 u7 chit8-phang5 chhin-chhiuN7 i chit-khoan2 e5 po2-siu2-phai3, cha2 chiu7 tui3 pun2-thou2-hoa3 chin chhi3-chhak8. Hian7-chai7 tioh8 i hoaN7 thong-sek kho3-theng5. I siong3-chun2 goa2 put-ko3 si7 chit8-e5 kiam-jim7 kang2-su, si7 kau3-su kai-chan5-lai7 siong7-ke7 chan5-chhu3--e5, chiu7 so2-teng7 goa2 he7-chhiu2. 
  Na7 hoe5-siong2 ti7 Gi7-siu2 Tai7-hak8 khui Tai5-gi2-kho3 chin khi-khiau e5 koe3-theng5, kam2-khai3 chiu7 na2 chhim. 2000 ni5 4--goeh8, chhou-chhou sin-chheng2 e5 si5, goa2 iong7 “Hian7-tai7 Tai5-gi2 Bun5-hak8” cho3 kho3-mia5, in-ui7 kiaN-liau2 koe3-thau5 chhi3-kek po2-siu2-phai3 sim2-cha ui2-oan5, ma7 siuN7 beh pi7-bian2 kap leng7-goa7 chit8-ui7 ka3 ia7-kan-pou7 Tai5-gi2 e5 lau7-su seng3-chit siuN oa2. Ko2-jian5 hit-si5 e5 thong-sek ui2-oan5-hoe7 tui3 “Tai5-gi2” che 2 ji7 chiu7 u7 i3-kian3. Ui7-tioh8 beh theh8 khui-kho3-koan5, lou7-boe2 goa2 chiu7 in, ka7 kho3-mia5 kai2-cho3 “Tai5-oan5 Bun5-hak8 chok-phin2 siau7-kai3”. Tng teh hoaN-hi2 tah8-chhut thau5-chit8-pou7, bo5 gi5-gou7 heng5-cheng3 jin5-oan5 soah ka7 siong7-kho3 si5-kan pai5 m7-tioh8, ti3-kau3 te7 1 pai2 khui-kho3, chiu7 in-ui7 hak8-seng bo5 kau3-giah8 lai5 theng5-khui. 
  Ka-chai3 soa3-chiap 2 hak8-ki5 khui u7-seng5. Goa2 chit8-bin7 ka3 Lo5-ma2-ji7, chit8-bin7 chhoa7 hak8-seng thak8 Tai5-gi2 chok-phin2. In kam2-kak beh oh8 e5 mih8 siuN-choe7, hu7-tam siuN tang7. Au7-lai5 goa2 eng7 “Ki-chhou2 Tai5-gi2” cho3 kho3-mia5, teng5-thau5 sin-chheng2, phah sng3 choan-sim ka3 Lo5-ma2-ji7 chiu7 ho2. Thong-sek ui2-oan5-hoe7 iu5-goan5 u7 i3-kian3. Put-ko3 kai2 kho3-mia5 liau2 chiu7 tong5-i3 hou7 goa2 khui-kho3. Chit-hak8-ki5 e5 hak8-seng pi2 eng2-koe3 khah choe7, theng5-tou7 ma7 khah ho2, khah chiau5. Chiah ka3 poaN3-hak8-ki5, tng teh jiat8-phut-phut e5 si5, soah lai5 hoat-seng “Jim7 Sian7-liong5 Su7-kiaN7”. 
